{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013bbrbAFYwxaTioWq2x1Gsm","type":"tool_result","content":"632\t### Story 9.2: Custom Workflow Creation\n633\t\n634\tAs a developer,\n635\tI want to create a custom workflow YAML in my project,\n636\tSo that I can define non-standard execution flows.\n637\t\n638\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n639\t\n640\t**Given** custom workflow at .codeharness/workflows/my-workflow.yaml\n641\t**When** `codeharness run --workflow my-workflow` executes\n642\t**Then** custom workflow loaded, validated, and executed\n643\t**And** must pass JSON schema validation\n644\t**And** agent references resolve through same config chain\n645\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01ChyoLDPrvpbR13hYNAz6e8","session_id":"c2800ecc-75a3-43b2-b3d8-396855aa3c3c","uuid":"3a3a060d-0c06-4d69-936a-96fcf9512958","timestamp":"2026-04-03T03:04:10.659Z"}
